{"tid":1874003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣宣道會海濱堂今午派發口罩 呼籲讓缺乏口罩者領取","createTime":"2020-02-11T03:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T04:57:55.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"47d7c7bbab2e6d8af0587fa03b5388df25828adb","tid":1874003,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://christiantimes.org.hk/News/161154/markphoto.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchristiantimes.org.hk%2FNews%2F161154%2Fmarkphoto.jpg&h=5b16bc8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【時代論壇訊】近日口罩供應短缺，位於荃灣海濱花園的宣道會海濱堂希望與港人一起共渡時艱，將於今日（2月11日）下午派發八千四百個口罩予本港缺乏口罩的居民，每位取得籌號的市民可獲發一包十個的口罩，醫護人員可優先獲贈。該堂特別呼籲信徒將消息傳給有需要人士，並希望大眾能讓缺乏口罩者領取，不要剝奪有需要人士獲贈的機會。<br />\n<br />\n該堂發放的相關資訊如下：<br />\n<br />\n荃灣宣道會海濱堂本著耶穌基督的關愛教導，2月11日週二送贈8,400個口罩予香港永久性居民（需出示個人身份證），每位一包（10個）。希望藉此與港人一起共渡時艱。<br />\n<br />\n詳細內容及條款如下：<br />\n<br />\nA. 對象：1. 醫護人員優先獲贈（需出示工作證）。2. 缺乏口罩人士（請不要剝奪有需要人士獲贈的機會）。<br />\nB. 日期：2月11日（週二）<br />\nC. 派籌時間：下午2時<br />\nD. 派籌次序：1.醫護人員  2.其他需要者<br />\nE. 派籌地點：荃灣海濱花園怡康街1-7號133舖地下<br />\nF.  派口罩時間：下午3時<br />\nG. 必須親臨領取，不得代領。<br />\nH. 所有獲贈的口罩不得轉售。<br />\n<br />\n品牌：ONEMED<br />\n類別：3層成人耳掛式外科口罩。<br />\n過濾效能：BFE&gt;99%<br />\n包裝： 1包10個（非獨立包裝）<br />\n出產地：印尼<br />\n<br />\n願主耶穌祝福大家身心安康！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://christiantimes.org.hk/Common/Reader/News/ShowNews.jsp?Nid=161154&amp;Pid=102&amp;Version=0&amp;Cid=2141&amp;Charset=big5_hkscs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchristiantimes.org.hk%2FCommon%2FReader%2FNews%2FShowNews.jsp%3FNid%3D161154%26Pid%3D102%26Version%3D0%26Cid%3D2141%26Charset%3Dbig5_hkscs&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=6dea9784\" target=\"_blank\">https://christiantimes.org.hk/Common/Reader/News/ShowNews.jsp?Nid=161154&amp;Pid=102&amp;Version=0&amp;Cid=2141&amp;Charset=big5_hkscs</a>"},{"pid":"03e5423552664ec5f6b78cdca6412cfc0a645788","tid":1874003,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c679166f4920d02a9ad409ca784f86bac8502f","tid":1874003,"uid":86204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:59:54.000Z","msg":"廢老大軍出動排隊"},{"pid":"c046a49e8eb8a12d2b7b4f853c46d1fbcc249a91","tid":1874003,"uid":313137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:10:15.000Z","msg":"要俾有需要人士呀!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15df987c1a69d38f05d60c52e9d2566cbbc5278e","tid":1874003,"uid":313137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:27:25.000Z","msg":"P牌推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00bd88258f75ecbb5b163aeb51bde0639c09972c","tid":1874003,"uid":69391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:38:53.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇落有百幾二百人掛緊"},{"pid":"6c05c3fdf0aa015230c80d904d1836881860de8e","tid":1874003,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00bd88258f75ecbb5b163aeb51bde0639c09972c","tid":1874003,"uid":69391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:38:53.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇落有百幾二百人掛緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T04:57:55.000Z","msg":"即係仲有位"}]}